/images/i/18909579.png" alt=""/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The&nbsp;<strong>VirtualBox</strong>&nbsp;will ask you where the ISO file downloaded by you in the previous step is.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://o7planning.org/en/11883/cache/images/i/18909625.png" alt=""/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>OK, at this time, the operating system starts being installed. If you are familiar with the installation of&nbsp;<strong>windows&nbsp;</strong>operating system, this is very simple.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://o7planning.org/en/11883/cache/images/i/18909712.png" alt=""/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://o7planning.org/en/11883/cache/images/i/18909741.png" alt=""/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://o7planning.org/en/11883/cache/images/i/18909785.png" alt=""/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://o7planning.org/en/11883/cache/images/i/18909818.png" alt=""/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://o7planning.org/en/11883/cache/images/i/18909820.png" alt=""/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://o7planning.org/en/11883/cache/images/i/18910118.png" alt=""/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Enter password and hint. Your hinted information helps you remember the password if you forget it in the future.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://o7planning.org/en/11883/cache/images/i/18910160.png" alt=""/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://o7planning.org/en/11883/cache/images/i/18910194.png" alt=""/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Select time and time zone:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://o7planning.org/en/11883/cache/images/i/18910245.png" alt=""/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://o7planning.org/en/11883/cache/images/i/18910247.png" alt=""/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Windows is installed!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://o7planning.org/en/11883/cache/images/i/18910313.png" alt=""/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'Install Oracle VM VirtualBox for IE10', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '883-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-10-16 04:00:20', '2019-10-16 04:00:20', '', 883, 'http://wiki.christinewilson.ca/883-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
